      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">225.7006-4</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a)  Use the provision at <ph xtrc="DFARxref" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref "
                     base="i1382344"
                     href="252.225-7037.dita#DFARS-252.225-7037">252.225-7037</xref>
            </ph>, Evaluation of Offers for Air Circuit Breakers, in solicitations, including solicitations using <ph xtrc="FARxref" class="- topic/ph ">FAR part 12</ph> procedures for the acquisition of commercial items, that require air circuit breakers for naval vessels unless—</p>
